def is_target_fork(fork:item):
    # Check if the instance is a fork item
    return is_fork(fork)

behavior wash_forks_by_hand(fork:item, sink:item):
    body:
        achieve close_char(char, fork)
        # Approach the fork to wash it

        achieve_once inhand(fork)
        # Hold the fork for washing

        achieve inside(fork, sink)
        # Place the fork in the sink
        
        wash(fork)
        # Wash the fork by hand

behavior __goal__():

            is_sink(sink) and id[sink] == 231
            # Select sink with ID 231 which was found in previous subtasks

        bind dining_room_201: item where:

                wash_forks_by_hand(fork, sink)

        achieve inside(o, sink)
        # Place the fork inside the sink

        wash(o) # Wash the fork
